window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>The Constable: The Complete Series</i> contains both Books 1 and 2 in The Constable series.</p> <p>My name is Alphonse Malloy, and I see everything.</p> <p>From a simple glance, I know your hobbies, what you ate for breakfast, how well you slept, and whether or not your wife is secretly seeing the high school biology teacher when you're not around.</p> <p>I can't explain how or why I get these feelings, only that I know they're true. All the little secrets you're too afraid to tell.</p> <p>Sometimes, that means helping people. Other times, it means staring down the barrel of a loaded gun.</p> <p>I wish I could tell you I was using this ability for good.</p> <p>I wish I could tell you a lot of things.</p> <p><b>Experience this exciting story set in the Renegade Star universe, featuring everyone's favorite Constable. If you're a fan of Sherlock Holmes, House M.D., Altered Carbon, or Renegade Star, you'll love this sci-fi thriller.</b></p>"; 
